VoxKey — Third-Party Licenses / 第三方许可与署名
===================================================

This product bundles or downloads the following third-party components. The
full license texts follow this summary.

1. FunASR (code) — Apache License 2.0
   Source: https://github.com/modelscope/FunASR
   Used for: local speech recognition (SenseVoice) executed through ONNX
   Runtime's Core ML Execution Provider on the Apple Neural Engine.
   Modification: the SenseVoiceSmall encoder is exported to ONNX (int8
   quantized) for the Apple Neural Engine. See the modification note below.

2. FunASR model weights — SenseVoiceSmall — FunASR Model Open Source License
   v1.1 (Alibaba Group). See "FunASR MODEL_LICENSE" below. Redistribution
