   The software is provided for reference and learning purposes.

3. Qwen3-ASR weights (0.6B, GGUF) — Apache License 2.0
   Source: https://huggingface.co/nzyaltair/Qwen3-ASR-0.6B-gguf
   Used for: local GPU (Metal) transcription via llama.cpp.

4. llama.cpp / llama-cpp-python — MIT License
   Source: https://github.com/ggerganov/llama.cpp
   Used for: Metal backend inference of the Qwen3-ASR GGUF weights.

