Modification notice (Apache License 2.0, Section 4(b))
------------------------------------------------------------

VoxKey modifies the FunASR SenseVoiceSmall encoder by exporting it to ONNX
(int8 quantization) for execution on the Apple Neural Engine via ONNX
Runtime's Core ML Execution Provider. The original model weights remain under
the FunASR Model Open Source License v1.1; the conversion is performed
locally by convert_funasr_coreml.py.
